\id JAS Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular 
\mt1 ﾆ、TAKURU YAAQUUBA NDUN 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Salminaango an min Yaaquuba, oo jiyaaﾉ熔 Alla e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on, haa e ﾉ擁i *bolondaaji sappoo e ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 saakitiiﾉ擁 e nder aduna on. 
\s1 Fii Wakkilagol Tampereeji 
\p  
\v 2 Ko onon yo musiﾉ橡兎, si on rewrii e kala noone ndarndanﾉ容, haray jogitoree ﾉ蓉n weltaare fow,  
\v 3 ko fii hiﾉ熔n andi, ndarndagol gomﾉ擁nal mon ngal adday ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲaare.  
\v 4 Kono bee ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲaare nden waﾉ預 golle timmuﾉ容, fii no woniron mokobaaﾉ兎 timmuﾉ兎, e hara on ﾅ蟻kkiraaka huunde.  
\v 5 Si goﾉ遼熔 e mon ﾅ蟻kkira faamu, yo o toro ﾉ蓉n Alla, on okkay mo ﾉ蓉n. Ko fii kanko Alla ko Yeﾉ熔owo fow no yaajiri e ﾉ殿awo feloore.  
\v 6 Kono yo o toror mo gomﾉ擁nal ngal aldaa e sikkitaare. Ko fii on sikkitiiﾉ熔 no wa'i wa morlooﾉ容 ndiyan ﾉ預n ka baharu, ﾉ容 hendu ndun duﾉｲata ﾆｴeﾆｴa.  
\v 7 Wota sifa on neﾉ遼熔 sikku hendoto goﾉ遼蓉n e juuﾉ容 Joomiraaﾉ熔 on,  
\v 8 on ko neﾉ遼熔 sikkitiiﾉ熔, mo tabitaa e laawi mun ﾉ擁n fow. 
\p  
\v 9 Yo musiﾉ遼熔 miskiino on weltor ko Alla towni mo kon,  
\v 10 alﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 on kadi weltora ko Alla tippini mo kon, ﾉ殿y fii makko on feﾆｴﾆｴiray wa piindi ngesa.  
\v 11 Si naange ngen fuﾉ擁i, nge toowidii e nguleendi magge muusundi ndin, hinge yornude kuﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, piindi majji on saama, ﾅ蟻ri majji on bonta, ko non alﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n saamirta e nder golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n. 
\p  
\v 12 Maloore wonanii on neﾉ遼熔 ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲiiﾉ熔 ndarndanﾉ容 ﾉ容n, ko fii si o dartike ndarndanﾉ容 ﾉ容n, o hendoto *meetelol ngurndan, ngol Joomiraaﾉ熔 on fodi yiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n. 
\p  
\v 13 Wota hay gooto wi'u e nder ko jarribetee kon: ﾂｫKo Alla jarribii mi.ﾂｻ Ko fii Alla jarribortaake ko boni, kanko kadi o jarribotaako hay gooto.  
\v 14 Nde jarribaﾉ容n woo, ko himmeeji bonﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 wonduﾉ容n ﾉ擁n woni en pooﾉ蓉de murtina.  
\v 15 ﾆ∥wto ﾉ蓉n, himme bonﾉ熔 on fuﾉ預 haa rima junuubu, si junuubu on kadi heewii, o rima mayde. 
\p  
\v 16 Wota on ﾉ預ynito, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an yiﾉ預aﾉ兎,  
\v 17 kala dokkal moﾆｴﾆｴal e kala dokkal timmungal ko ka dow iwrani en, e immorde e Baabaajo ndayguuji ﾉ擁n, on mo waylotaako, mo ﾉ熔wdi mun dillataa,  
\v 18 on Woodintinirﾉ熔 en Daaluyee makko goongaajo on no o yiﾉ擁ri non, fii no laatoren dikkuruuﾉ兎 e tagu makko ngun. 
\s1 Fii Huutorgol Daaluyee Alla on 
\p  
\v 19 Andee ﾉ蓉n, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an yiﾉ預aﾉ兎, yo neﾉ遼熔 kala yaawu heﾉ預ade, nenna si yewta, nenna si tikka.  
\v 20 Ko fii tikkannde neﾉ遼預nke nden laatintaa peewal ngal Alla yiﾉ擁 ngal.  
\v 21 Awa sertee e kala ko tuuninta e kala bonki layuki, jaﾉ妬ron newaare daaluyee aawaaﾉ熔 e mon on, ﾉ蓉n ko on waawuﾉ熔 dandude wonkiiji mon ﾉ擁n. 
\p  
\v 22 Wonee huutorooﾉ兎 daaluyee on, hara hinaa on heﾉ熔tooﾉ兎 mo tun, si hinaa ﾉ蓉n, haray onon tigi on ﾉ預ynitoto woni.  
\v 23 Ko fii si goﾉ遼熔 heﾉ擁ke daaluyee on, o huutoraali mo, haray himo wa'i wa neﾉ遼熔 wonﾉ熔 tintaade, yi'a yeeso mun ngon.  
\v 24 Si o gaynii ndaaritaade, o yahii, o yejjita kisan ko honno o wa'i.  
\v 25 Kono on waﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 giiﾉ容 mun ﾉ容n ka nder sariya timmuﾉ熔, ﾉ蓉n ko on sariya rinﾉ擁noowo, o tabiti, hara hinaa fii heﾉ預gol yejjita, kono hara ko huutorgol, onﾉ熔n wonay malaaﾉ熔 e nder kala ko o waﾉ預ta. 
\p  
\v 26 On mo sikki ko dewo, e ﾉ殿awo waawugol ﾉ容nngal mun ngal, haray on ﾉ預ynii hoore mun, ngal dewal ko meerewal.  
\v 27 Dewal laaﾉ砥ngal, ngal aldaa e koju ngal yeeso Alla Baabaajo on, ko dankagol aliyatiimaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e dankagol keynguuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e nder satteendeeji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, e rentagol e tuundiiji aduna ﾉ擁n. 
\c 2  
\s1 Hajagol fii ﾆ「rdindingol 
\p  
\v 1 Musiﾉ橡兎 an, ﾉ殿y ko on gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men mo darja wonani on, reenee e ﾉ砥rdindingol yimﾉ兎.  
\v 2 Si wattiiﾉ熔 hurundaare kaﾅ暁菊, ﾉ登rnii conci dimi aru e naatude ka *moftal mon, baaso kadi ﾉ登rniiﾉ熔 conci yakkiiﾉ擁 ara e naatude,  
\v 3 si on hittinii fii ﾉ登rniiﾉ熔 conci dimi on, on wi'ii mo: ﾂｫOnon toolii mon ka ndaﾉ遼蓉di ﾉ熔o!ﾂｻ, wi'on baaso on: ﾂｫAn daro ﾉ預a!ﾂｻ, maa: ﾂｫJooﾉ熔 ka ley koyﾉ容 an ﾉ熔o!ﾂｻ,  
\v 4 e hara on waﾉ預ali sendondiral hakkunde mon onon tigi? E on ﾉｲaawiraali miijooji bonﾉ擁? 
\p  
\v 5 Heﾉ擁tee, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an yiﾉ預aﾉ兎! E hara hinaa miskinﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka aduna ﾉ熔o Alla suﾉ妬i fii no ﾉ兎 wonira alﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 e nder gomﾉ擁nal ngal, e heﾉ登oﾉ兎 geﾉ殿l e laamu ngu o fodi yiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n ngun?  
\v 6 Kono onon, on hersinii baaso on. E hara wonaa alﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n woni on tampinde, naﾉ殿 on ka ﾉｲaawirﾉ擁?  
\v 7 E hinaa ﾉ兎n woni hoynooﾉ兎 innde teddunde nde inniraﾉ熔n nden? 
\p  
\v 8 Kono si on ﾉ熔ftike sariya mawﾉ熔 on, wano bindi ﾉ擁n wi'iri non wonde: ﾂｫYo a yiﾉ擁r ﾉｲokondo maa on wano yiﾉ擁rﾉ預a hoore maa nonﾂｻ,\f a \fr 2:8 \ft 2.8 Lew. 19.18 \f* haray on waﾉ擁i ko moﾆｴﾆｴi.  
\v 9 Kono si on ﾉ砥rdindinii yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, haray on waﾉ擁i junuubu, Sariya on no jogori on wa bonnuﾉ熔 Sariya.  
\v 10 Ko ﾉ蓉n waﾉ擁, on mo yeddi yamiroore wootere e nder Sariya on, hay si o ﾉ熔ftike ﾉ容ya heddiiﾉ容 fow, haray o wonii bonnuﾉ熔 Sariya on fow.  
\v 11 Ko fii on Wi'uﾉ熔: ﾂｫwota mo jeenaﾂｻ, no wi'i kadi: ﾂｫwota mo itta hoore.ﾂｻ E hin-le si on waﾉ預ali jinaa, kono on ittii hoore, haray on wonii bonnuﾉ熔 Sariya on. 
\p  
\v 12 Awa yewtiree huuwiron wa yimﾉ兎 ﾉｲaawiroyteeﾉ兎 Sariya rinﾉ擁noowo on.  
\v 13 Ko fii ﾉｲaawoore nden aldanaa mo yurmetaake e yurmeende, kono yurmeende nden foolay ﾉｲaawoore nden. 
\s1 Fii Hakkunde Gomﾉ擁nal e Kuugal 
\p  
\v 14 Musiﾉ橡兎 an, ko nafa honﾉ蓉n woodani neﾉ遼熔 wi'ugol himo mari gomﾉ擁nal, si o alaa ﾉ殿nginirde ﾉ蓉n kuuﾉ容? Taw si sifa ngal gomﾉ擁nal no waawi dandude mo?  
\v 15 Si musiﾉ遼熔 men gorko maa bandiraawo men no holi, no ﾅ蟻kkiri ﾉｲaametee kadi ﾉｲande woo,  
\v 16 goﾉ遼熔 e mon ara e wi'ude ﾉ兎n: ﾂｫYahee e jam, ﾉ登rnoﾉ熔n, ﾉｲaamon haa haaronﾂｻ, e ﾉ殿awo jonnugol ﾉ兎 ko ﾉ殿lli maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n handi e mun kon, haray ko honﾉ蓉n ﾉ蓉n nafata?  
\v 17 Gomﾉ擁nal ngal kadi ko wano non: si ngal aldaa e kuuﾉ容, ko ngal mayngal kangal tigi. 
\p  
\v 18 Kono si goﾉ遼熔 wi'ii: ﾂｫAn hiﾉ預 mari gomﾉ擁nal e min miﾉ熔 mari kuuﾉ容ﾂｻ, haray min mi wi'ay mo: ﾂｫHollan gomﾉ擁nal maa ngal e ﾉ殿awo kuuﾉ容, min non mi hollirte gomﾉ擁nal an ngal kuuﾉ容 an ﾉ容n.ﾂｻ  
\v 19 Hiﾉ預 gomﾉ擁ni ko Alla gooto woodi? No moﾆｴﾆｴi! Jinnaaji ﾉ擁n kadi no gomﾉ擁niri non, haa hiﾉ擁 diwna. 
\p  
\v 20 Ko an yo njofoojo! Hiﾉ預 faalaa faamude wonde gomﾉ擁nal ngal aldaa e kuuﾉ容 ko meerewal? 
\p  
\v 21 Enee, wonaa ko Ibraahiima, on maamiraawo men, waﾉ蓉noo kon fewndo o weeﾉ妬ti *Issaaqa ﾉ妬ﾉ遼熔 makko on fii layyagol ka *layyorde kon waﾉ擁 si o jogitoraa feewuﾉ熔?  
\v 22 A yi'ii, gomﾉ擁nal ngal yaadii e kuuﾉ容 makko ﾉ容n, awa kadi ko kuuﾉ容 makko ﾉ容n timmini gomﾉ擁nal makko ngal.  
\v 23 Ko non ko bindi ﾉ擁n wi'i kon laatori: ﾂｫIbraahiima gomﾉ擁ni Alla, ngal gomﾉ擁nal makko jogoranaa mo peewalﾂｻ, haa o noddaa giﾉ熔 Alla.  
\v 24 On yi'ii, ko sabu kuuﾉ容 ﾉ容n neﾉ遼熔 on jogoraa feewuﾉ熔, hinaa sabu gomﾉ擁nal ngal tun. 
\p  
\v 25 Enee, oo cagaajo wi'eteeﾉ熔 *Raabi, kanko kadi, taw si hinaa sabu kuuﾉ容 ﾉ容n o jogoranoo feewuﾉ熔 fewndo ko o wernunoo nulanooﾉ兎 fii tefugol ﾉ兎n, o holli ﾉ兎 laawol goo ngol ﾉ兎 rewa?  
\v 26 Wano tawiri non ﾉ殿ndu ndu aldaa e ruuhu ko mayndu, ko wano non kadi gomﾉ擁nal ngal aldaa e kuuﾉ容 ko mayngal. 
\c 3  
\s1 Fii Huﾉ妬ndagol ﾆ各nngal 
\p  
\v 1 Musiﾉ橡兎 an, wota buy e mon himman jannugol, ko fii hiﾉ熔n andi enen jannooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n en ﾉｲaawete ﾉｲaawoore ﾉ砥rnde sattude.  
\v 2 Ko fii en fow en waﾉ預y ellaaji ﾉ擁 tawata ko nooneeji ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ擁. On mo waﾉ預ali ella e nder konguﾉ擁, haray on neﾉ遼熔 ko timmuﾉ熔, waawuﾉ熔 huﾉ妬ndaade ﾉ殿ndu mun ndun fow. 
\p  
\v 3 Si en waﾉ擁i lagambe ﾉ容n ka kundule pucci ﾉ擁n fii yo ﾉ擁 ﾉ熔fto en, haray en huutoray kadi ﾉ殿lli majji on fow.  
\v 4 Ndaaree kadi, ﾉ容e laaﾉ容 e njanﾉ蓉de mun, ko hendu dolnundu naﾉ殿ta ﾉ容, hiﾉ容 ardoree aalahun ﾉ砥rkun fanﾉ蓉de ka naﾉ登owo on faaliraa ﾉ熔n.  
\v 5 Wano non, ﾉ容nngal kadi ko terun fanﾉ蓉kun, kono hingal waawi mantorde piiji mawﾉ擁. On yi'ii wano giitun tosokun waawi sunnirde buruure mawnde?  
\v 6 ﾆ各nngal ngal kadi ko yiite, hingal heewi boneeji, hingal tawdaa e tere ﾉ殿ndu men ndun, ngal tuuninay ﾉ殿ndu ndun fow, ko ka yiite jahannama ngal huﾉ橡妬naa, ngal sunnay ngurndan men ﾉ預n fow. 
\p  
\v 7 Kala noone kulle, wano colli ﾉ擁n e ko daasotoo kon e kulle ﾉ容n ka nder ndiyan, no huﾉ妬ndoo, ﾉ容n-le neﾉ遼預nke no huﾉ妬ndii ﾉ容.  
\v 8 Kono ﾉ容nngal, hay gooto waawataa ngal huﾉ妬ndaade. Ko bone mo waawotaako huﾉ妬ndaade, hingal heewi tooke warooje.  
\v 9 Ko kangal mantirten Ben men Joomiraaﾉ熔 on, ko kangal kadi huﾉ擁rten yimﾉ兎 tagaaﾉ兎 e mbaadi Alla ﾉ兎n.  
\v 10 Ko e kon hunduko wooto du'aa e kuddi yaltata. Kono yo musiﾉ橡兎, wota ﾉ蓉n wonir non.  
\v 11 Taw si ndiyan welﾉ預n e ndiyan haaﾉ蓉ﾉ預n no tubba e ﾉ砥ndu wooturu, hara ko e ngayka woota?  
\v 12 Enee musiﾉ橡兎 an, hara ﾆｴibbehi no waawi rimude kaccu, maa piyahi rima ﾆｴibbe? Ko wano non kadi, ﾉ砥ndu ndiyan lanﾉ預n waawataa tubbinde ndiyan welﾉ預n. 
\s1 Fii Faamu Iwrungu ka Dow ngun 
\p  
\v 13 Ko hombo e hakkunde mon mari faamu e hakkil? Yo o ﾉ殿nginir ﾉ蓉n jikku makko moﾆｴﾆｴo on wondude e kuuﾉ容 newiiﾉ容 iwruﾉ容 e faamu.  
\v 14 Kono si tawii hiﾉ熔n mari ka ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mon nawliigu tiiﾉ蓉ngu e haasidi, haray wota on mawnintino, e wota on yeddu goonga on.  
\v 15 Sifa ngun faamu hinaa ka kammu iwri few, ko ngu aduna e ngu neﾉ遼預nke e ngu Ibuliisa.  
\v 16 Ko fii, kala ka nawliigu e haasidi woni, ko ﾉ熔n kadi jiiﾉ登ldu e kala noone kuuﾉ容 bonﾉ容 woni.  
\v 17 Kono faamu iwrungu ka Alla ngun, ko adii taho, ko ngu laaﾉ砥ngu, awa kadi ko ngu ﾉ砥ttu, ko ngu newiingu, ko ngu deeﾆｴinayngu, heewungu yurmeende e kuuﾉ容 moﾆｴﾆｴe, ngu aldaa e ﾉ砥rnondiral e faasiqankaaku.  
\v 18 Ko tabintinooﾉ兎 ﾉ砥ttu ﾉ兎n aawata e nder ﾉ砥ttu kon, rimay peewal. 
\c 4  
\s1 Fii ﾆ覚ftagol Alla, Yankinanoo Mo 
\p  
\v 1 Ko honto ﾉ容e poodotire e ﾉ容e yeddondire hakkunde mon iwri? E hara hinaa faaleeji bonﾉ擁 woni waﾉ蓉de hare ka ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mon?  
\v 2 Hiﾉ熔n himmani, kono on alaa heﾉ砥de. Ko on warooﾉ兎, ko on miilaaﾉ兎 e ﾉ殿awo waawugol heﾉ砥de hay huunde. Hiﾉ熔n wondi e yeddondire e pooﾉ熔tiro. E hin-le on hendotaako, ﾉ殿y on alaa toraade,  
\v 3 maa hiﾉ熔n toraade, on alaa heﾉ砥de, ﾉ殿y hiﾉ熔n tororde anniyee bonﾉ熔 fii no huutoriron ﾉ蓉n fii faaleeji mon. 
\p  
\v 4 Ko onon, yo jamaa jinooﾉ兎! E on andaa yiﾉ蓉gol aduna on ko aﾉｲugol Alla? Awa si goﾉ遼熔 no faalaa yiﾉ蓉de aduna on, haray o waﾉ擁tike gaﾉｲo Alla.  
\v 5 On sikku bindi ﾉ擁n ko wi'i kon ko meere, wonde: ﾂｫAlla no nawlani ruuhu mo o waﾉ擁 e men on.ﾂｻ?\f b \fr 4:5 \ft 4.5 Maa: \+it ﾂｫRuuhu wonﾉ熔 ka ﾉ兎rnde men on ko nawluﾉ熔 fota.ﾂｻ\+it*\f* 
\v 6 Kono ko o ﾉ砥ri en yeﾉ蓉de e ko mawni kon ko sulfu. Awa e hino ko bindi ﾉ擁n wi'i kon: 
\q1 ﾂｫAlla liddoto mawnintiniiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, 
\q1 o yeﾉ預 jippinﾉ兎 hoore mun ﾉ兎n sulfu.ﾂｻ\f c \fr 4:6 \ft 4.6 Tin. 3.34 \f* 
\m  
\v 7 Awa yankinanee Alla, dartoﾉ熔n Ibuliisa, ﾉ蓉n o dogay, o woﾉ遼熔o on.  
\v 8 ﾆ∥dee Alla, ﾉ蓉n o ﾉ殿doto on. Laﾉ橡妬nee juuﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n, yo onon junuubankeeﾉ兎. Laﾉ橡妬non ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n, yo onon sikkitiiﾉ兎.  
\v 9 Woytee, yoomon, wullon. Yo jaleeﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n wontu yoomugol, weltaare mon nden wonta ﾉ妬ﾉ預gol.  
\v 10 Jippinee hoore mon yeeso Joomiraaﾉ熔 on, ﾉ蓉n o ﾉ殿ntoyay on. 
\p  
\v 11 Wota on ﾉｲakkin ﾉ兎e ﾉ熔o maa ﾉ兎e ﾉ預a, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an. Mo ﾉｲakkinii musiﾉ遼熔 mun, maa ﾉｲaawii musiﾉ遼熔 mun, haray ko Sariya on o ﾉｲakkini, o ﾉｲaawi. Si a ﾉｲaawii-le Sariya on, haray hinaa a huutorﾉ熔 mo, kono ko a ﾉｲaawoowo mo.  
\v 12 Ko fii ko Gooto pet woni Waﾉ熔owo Sariya ﾉｲaawa, ﾉ蓉n ko on Waawuﾉ熔 dandude e mulude. An non, ko a hombo, si hiﾉ預 ﾉｲaawa ﾉｲokondo maa? 
\s1 Fii Mawnintinaare e Townitaare 
\p  
\v 13 Ko onon, yo wi'uﾉ兎 jooni: ﾂｫHande maa jango men yahay e ndee saare ﾉ熔o, men wona ton hitaande, men waﾉ熔ya ton goﾉ遼蓉n, men heﾉ殿 tono.ﾂｻ  
\v 14 Onon on andaa toode no ngurndan mon ﾉ預n wonirta jango. Ko on norngal feeﾉｲungal fii saa'ihun nii, ﾉ殿wto ﾉ蓉n muta.  
\v 15 Ko haanuﾉ熔n wi'ude: ﾂｫMen wuuray, men waﾉ預 ﾉ蓉nﾉ熔o maa ﾉ蓉nﾉ預a, si Joomiraaﾉ熔 on jaﾉ妬i.ﾂｻ  
\v 16 Kono jooni, hiﾉ熔n mawnintinaade e nder townitaare mon. Sifa nden mawnintinaare fow ko bonnde.  
\v 17 Si goﾉ遼熔 no andi moﾆｴﾆｴere nde o haani waﾉ蓉de, o waﾉ預ali ﾉ蓉n, haray o waﾉ擁i junuubu. 
\c 5  
\s1 Fii Hajagol Alﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n 
\p  
\v 1 Jooni non, yo onon alﾉ蓉ﾉ兎, wullee sowru tiiﾉ蓉ndu, sabu tampereeji aroyayﾉ擁 e hoore mon ﾉ擁n!  
\v 2 Ngalu mon ngun bonii, conci mon ﾉ擁n mooﾆｴii,  
\v 3 kaﾅ暁菊 mon ﾉ容n e kaalisi mon on kornii. Kori mun on immoyto seeditoo e hoore mon, ﾉｲaamira ﾉ殿lli mon ﾉ擁n wa yiite. On mooﾉ妬i ngaluuji e nder ﾉ容e ﾉｲalaaﾉ容 sakkitore.  
\v 4 Njoddi ndi on yoﾉ殿ali wa'uﾉ兎 gese mon ﾉ容n ndin no woytaade e hoore mon. E woyaaﾉ擁 soﾉｲituﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n arii haa e noppi Joomiraaﾉ熔 Jom Bawﾉ容 on.  
\v 5 On wuuririi ka aduna ﾉ熔o e nder mbeleeﾉ容 e ko foti. On fayinii hoore mon e ndee ﾉｲalaande nde hirseteﾉ熔n e mun.  
\v 6 On ﾉｲaawii, on warii feewuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 dartaaki on. 
\s1 Fii Yondinaare 
\p  
\v 7 Awa muﾉｲﾉｲee, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an, haa nde Joomi on ari. Ndaaree no remoowo habbori coﾉｲal tiiﾉ蓉ngal, ngal o habbori muﾉｲal haa ndiyan setto e ndiyan dabbunde toﾉ橡殿.  
\v 8 Onon kadi muﾉｲﾉｲee, tabintinon ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mon ﾉ容n, ko fii ardu Joomi on ko ﾉ殿diiﾉ蓉n.  
\v 9 Wota on ﾅ菊rmindir, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an, fii wota on ﾉｲaawe, ﾉ殿y ﾆ拌awoowo on no darii ka yeeso dambugal. 
\p  
\v 10 Musiﾉ橡兎 an, ﾆｴettee misal tampere e muﾉｲal ﾉ兎n annabaaﾉ兎 yewtuﾉ兎 e innde Joomiraaﾉ熔 on.  
\v 11 Ndaaree, hiﾉ容n wi'a maloore wonanii ﾉ兎n ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲiiﾉ兎. On nanii fii ﾅ蟻ﾉｲﾉｲaare Ayyuuba nden no wowlee, awa kadi on yi'ii ko Joomiraaﾉ熔 on waﾉ預ni mo kon ka sakkitorun. Ko fii Joomiraaﾉ熔 on ko heewuﾉ熔 giggol e yurmeende. 
\p  
\v 12 Ko adii kon taho, yo musiﾉ橡兎 an, wota on woondir kammu ngun maa leydi ndin, maa kala ko woni e woondoore. Ko yo ﾂｫhiiyiiﾂｻ mon on wonu ﾂｫhiiyiiﾂｻ, ﾂｫoo'oﾂｻ mon on wona ﾂｫoo'oﾂｻ, fii wota on wonu e nder ﾉｲaawoore nden. 
\s1 Fii Tororgol Gomﾉ擁nal 
\p  
\v 13 E hara goﾉ遼熔 e mon no e nder tampere? Yo ontigi toro Alla. Kaa hara goﾉ遼熔 e mon no e nder weltaare? Yo ootigi beytu.  
\v 14 E hara kadi goﾉ遼熔 e mon no nawni? Yo ontigi noddu ardotooﾉ兎 *moftal ngal, ﾉ兎ntigi toranoo mo e hoore juurugol nebban e hoore makko e innde Joomiraaﾉ熔 on.  
\v 15 Toraare waﾉ擁raande gomﾉ擁nal no sellina nawnuﾉ熔. E hoore ﾉ蓉n, Joomiraaﾉ熔 on imminay mo. Si tawii ontigi no waﾉ擁 junuubi, ﾉ擁 yaafante mo.  
\v 16 Awa, qirritee junuubaaji mon ﾉ擁n hakkunde mon, torondiranon kadi, fii no sellinireﾉ熔n. Torndeeji ﾉ擁 aaden feewuﾉ熔 torii ﾉ擁n ko dolnuﾉ擁 duncayﾉ擁. 
\p  
\v 17 Ko fii Iiliiya kadi hari ko neﾉ遼熔 wa'unooﾉ熔 wa men nii, nde o duuminoo e toraare fii wota ndiyan aru, ﾉ預n ronki arude ka hoore leydi e nder duuﾉ妬 tati e lebbi jeegoo.  
\v 18 ﾆ∥wto ﾉ蓉n kadi o torii, kammu ngun sammini ndiyan, onsay leydi ndin funtini ko rimata ﾉ妬ﾉ橡兎. 
\p  
\v 19 Ko onon yo musiﾉ橡兎 an, si goﾉ遼熔 e hakkunde mon selii goonga on, goﾉ遼熔 artirii mo,  
\v 20 haray andee, on ittuﾉ熔 on junuubankeejo ka o selunoo ton, artiri mo ka laawol, haray o montii junuubaaji ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉ﾉ擁, o dandii wonkii mayde.